Ing '''Novial''' [''nov-'' ("new") + ''IAL, International Auxiliary Language''] metung yang [[w:international auxiliary language|amanung internacional a panyaup]]  a  [[w:constructed language|pikudta]] (constructed) (IAL, pamikuyad king Ingles) a melalang bang makasaup king pamiugnayan at pamikakaluguran dareng bansa a yalang mákalamáng o mayayagraviadu. Ing miglalang kaniti yapin i Profesor [[Otto Jespersen]], metung a [[e:linguist]] (matenakan kareng amanu) ibat [[Denmark]] a sadyang kayanib king pangimut a [[w:Ido]] at kaybat miyabe murin king pamaglalang king [[w:Interlingua]].

Keraklan kareng kataya na niti ibat la kareng amanung [[w:Germanic languages|Germanic]] at [[w:Romance languages|Romance]], kabang ing kaya naming garalita, dakal ne man kinwa king [[w:English language|Ingles]].

Minuna yang mipakilala ing Novial ketang libru nang Jespersen a ''An International Language'' kanitang [[1928]]. Mika pamagbayu ya ketang kayang diccionariu, ''Novial Lexike'', a milimbag kaybat ning adwang banwa. Mika karagdagang pamanaliwa ketang [[w:1930s|decadang 1930]], dapot mengapaburen ya kaybat ning kamatayan nang Jespersen anyang [[1943]]. Kanitang [[w:1990|decadang 1990]], dakal lang taung mekatuklas pasibayu king Novial anyang linto ya ing [[w:Internet|Aptas]].

